field_not_aggregatable.text: Field "{{fieldName}}" is not an aggregatable field.

cardinality_by_field.text: Cardinality of by_field "{{fieldName}}" is above 1000 and might result in high memory usage.

cardinality_over_field_low.text: Cardinality of over_field "{{fieldName}}" is below 10 and might be less suitable for population analysis.

cardinality_over_field_high.text: Cardinality of over_field "{{fieldName}}" is above 1000000 and might result in high memory usage.

cardinality_partition_field.text: Cardinality of partition_field "{{fieldName}}" is above 1000 and might result in high memory usage.

bucket_span_empty.text: The bucket span field must be specified.

bucket_span_estimation_mismatch.text: Current bucket span is "{{currentBucketSpan}}", but bucket span estimation returned "{{estimateBucketSpan}}".

bucket_span_high.text: Bucket span is 1 day or more. Be aware that days are considered as UTC days, not local days.

bucket_span_no_duration.text: Bucket span estimation was skipped because no start and end date to reference the original data was supplied. This is not yet available when using the advanced job config wizard.

bucket_span_invalid.text: The specified bucket span is not a valid time interval format e.g. 10m, 1h. It also needs to be higher than zero.

detectors_empty.text: No detectors were found. At least one detector must be specified.

detectors_function_empty.text: One of the detector functions is empty.

index_fields_invalid.text: Could not load fields from index.

influencer_high.text: The job configuration includes more than 3 influencers. Consider using fewer influencers or creating multiple jobs.

influencer_low.text: The job configuration includes no influencers. Picking an influencer is strongly recommended.

influencer_low_suggestion.text: The job configuration includes a partition or over field but no influencers are configured. Consider using {{influencerSuggestion}} as an influencer.

influencer_low_suggestions.text: The job configuration includes partition or over fields but no influencers are configured. Consider using one of {{influencerSuggestion}} as an influencer.

job_id_empty.text: The job name field must not be empty.

job_id_invalid.text: The job name is invalid. It can contain lowercase alphanumeric (a-z and 0-9) characters, hyphens or underscores and must start and end with an alphanumeric character.

job_group_id_invalid.text: One of the job group names is invalid. They can contain lowercase alphanumeric (a-z and 0-9) characters, hyphens or underscores and must start and end with an alphanumeric character.

skipped_extended_tests.text: Skipped some checks because the basic requirements of the job configuration were not met.
